abstract: Stocks rise on announcement by Federal Reserve it will not raise interest rates, with real estate and telecom making biggest gains.
lead_paragraph: Investors were pleased after the Federal Reserve kept its key interest rate unchanged and signaled that it was likely to rise later this year.

headline.main: Wall St. Closes Higher on Energy Gains
